         <div xml:id="alalal-a94887"><!-- l1d17dt2 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-a94887-Hd1e99">Divisio Textus</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-a94887-d1e101">
               <cb ed="#Ba" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#Ba" n="6"/>DIVISIO TEXTUS.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-a94887-d1e108">
               <lb ed="#Ba" n="7"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-a94887-Qd1e112"> Hic quaeritur, Si charitas Spiritus
<lb ed="#Ba" n="8"/>sanctus est, etc. </quote>
               <lb ed="#Ba" n="9"/>Hic incipit secunda pars istius 
distin<lb break="no" ed="#Ba" n="10"/>clionis, in qua Magister solvit contra se
<lb ed="#Ba" n="11"/>objecta. Et dividitur in tres partes : in
<lb ed="#Ba" n="12"/>quarum prima objicit per rationem et
<lb ed="#Ba" n="13"/>solvit. In secunda, objicit per 
auctorita<lb break="no" ed="#Ba" n="14"/>tes et solvit, ibi, L, <quote xml:id="alalal-a94887-Qd1e130"> Supra dictum est,
<lb ed="#Ba" n="15"/>quod Spiritus sanctus, etc. </quote> In tertia,
<lb ed="#Ba" n="16"/>objicit per unam auctoritatem, qua 
ma<lb break="no" ed="#Ba" n="17"/>xime videtur esse contra eum, et solvit,
<lb ed="#Ba" n="18"/>ibi, Q, <quote xml:id="alalal-a94887-Qd1e142"> Alias quoque inducunt 
ratio<lb break="no" ed="#Ba" n="19"/>nes, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-a94887-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#Ba" n="20"/>In prima parte sunt tria capitula, 
quo<lb break="no" ed="#Ba" n="21"/>rum primum habet objectionem : 
secun<lb break="no" ed="#Ba" n="22"/>dum, solutionem, ibi, H, <quote xml:id="alalal-a94887-Qd1e156"> His itaque
<lb ed="#Ba" n="23"/>respondemus, etc. </quote> Tertium, 
confirma<lb break="no" ed="#Ba" n="24"/>tionem solutionis, sicut patet in Lettera,
<lb ed="#Ba" n="25"/>ibi, K, <quote xml:id="alalal-a94887-Qd1e166"> Ut autem certius fiat, etc. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
